        file chooser, this is useful when using the -s cli option. Patch by
        Enrico Tröger.
    
    2009-02-08 jeromeg
    
      * configure.ac.in: add maintainer information about xml2po and
        xsltproc.
    
    2009-02-08 jeromeg
    
